I Got That Hey Papi (2000r.) Beyoncé singles chronology I Got That Work It Out (2002r.) "I Got That" is a single by rapper Amil featuring Beyoncé Knowles of Destiny's Child. It was the first single by Beyoncé and also it is currently the last solo single by Amil. Eve makes a cameo appearance in the video. == CD single == # "I Got That (Radio Edit)" (Whitehead, A./Barnes, Samuel/Lewis, LeShan/Smith, Tamy/Carter, Shawn/Olivier, Jean Claude "Poke"/Davis, Makeda) – 3:21 # "I Got That (Instrumental)" – 3:19 Category:Beyoncé songs Category:2000 songs
title: I Got That
